flowchart TB
  subgraph Browser
    UI[GitHub Pages Frontend]
  end

  subgraph DemoAccess[Public Demo Access]
    Tunnel[Cloudflare Tunnel HTTPS URL]
  end

  subgraph Kubernetes[Local kind / GKE Kubernetes]
    API[Go API Service\nAuth, CORS, Rate Limit, Status API]
    Kafka[Redpanda Kafka\nkyc_enroll / kyc_verify]
    Worker[Go Worker\nDedup + Decision Logic]
    Infer[Python Inference\nFace 512D + Name 768D + Liveness]
    Qdrant[Qdrant\nface_embeddings + name_embeddings]
    Redis[Redis\nstatus + secure metadata]
    Prom[Prometheus]
    Grafana[Grafana Dashboard]
  end

  UI -->|HTTPS fetch + Bearer token| Tunnel
  Tunnel --> API
  API -->|publish job| Kafka
  Kafka -->|consume job| Worker
  Worker -->|multipart image/name| Infer
  Worker -->|vector upsert/search| Qdrant
  Worker -->|status/result| Redis
  API -->|status read| Redis
  API --> Prom
  Worker --> Prom
  Prom --> Grafana
